News
====

The 2.6.1 point release rolls up the 2.6 fixes and adds feature request 40.

Note that recent versions of MbedTLS require that when verifiying a remote
server's certificate the server's CNAME should be defined. That means that
E-MailRelay's "--client-tls-verify" option also requires
"--client-tls-verify-name" if using MbedTLS.

